data.description: Fort Lauderdale beauty For Sale, just 4 miles from the beach. Beautiful kitchen, laundry room, and a split floor plan are some of its features. Nature enthusiasts will delight in the bird-watching opportunities, with captivating backyard views from every room, frequently seen are Blue Jays and Cardinals. Nestled in a friendly and pet-friendly neighborhood with sidewalks, ideal for families. Excellent schools nearby. Great restaurants and attractions just minutes away. For those who love outdoor gatherings, the covered back patio is perfect for hosting friends and family. The interior is bathed in natural light thanks to numerous windows, creating an inviting ambiance throughout the home. Large bedrooms offer ample living space, ensuring comfort and convenience. RV/Boat parking available.
